and continue after we perish.</i>

1056
01:27:44,299 --> 01:27:47,427
<i>Our lives and our choices</i>

1057
01:27:47,552 --> 01:27:52,933
<i>like quantum trajectories are
understood moment to moment</i>

1058
01:27:53,391 --> 01:27:58,188
<i>at each point of intersection,
each encounter,</i>

1059
01:27:58,313 --> 01:28:02,525
