1060
01:28:04,945 --> 01:28:07,072
<i>Proposition:</i>

1061
01:28:07,197 --> 01:28:10,450
<i>I have fallen in love with Luisa Rey.</i>

1062
01:28:11,618 --> 01:28:17,541
<i>Is this possible?
I just met her, and yet...</i>

1063
01:28:17,624 --> 01:28:23,630
